docs.lead_paragraph: Mrs. Littles, the Rochester murderess, is employed at Sing Sing State Prison in trimming hate. She conducts herself with propriety, and obeys the discipline of the Prison. The forger Huntington, in the same institution, is said to be one of the best of the prisoners. He is employed as book-keeper in the cabinetshop.

docs.lead_paragraph: A FEMALE FIGHT IN A GERMAN DANCE-HOUSE--ONE WOMAN STABBED.--At an early hour last evening, a quarrel ensued between JOHANNA VENT and CATHERINE BIDDLE, inmates of the German dance-house No. 103 Washington-street, during which Miss RIDDLE was stabbed and seriously injured by Miss VENT.

docs.lead_paragraph: The most important business transacted by the United States Senate yesterday was the passage of the French Spoliation bill, by a vote of 26 to 20, after elaborate speeches by Mr. DAVIS against it, and Mr. CRITTENDEN in its favor. Senator DOUGLAS appeared and took his seat for the first time during the session.

docs.lead_paragraph: THE MERCANTILE LIBRARY ASSOCIATION.--The Annual Election for officers of this Institution will be held on Tuesday, Jan. 18. There is just enough rivalry and jealousy existing among the members to make the proceedings interesting and the Society a live and useful one. At the first election, lone year ago, there were some who thought that a select few intended to rule and have their own way about everything.

docs.snippet: THE CITY INSPECTOR.--The most important of our municipal officers, so far as the health of the people and the general condition of the City are concerned, is, undoubtedly, the City Inspector. He is our Health Officer. Great power is placed in his...
docs.lead_paragraph: THE CITY INSPECTOR.--The most important of our municipal officers, so far as the health of the people and the general condition of the City are concerned, is, undoubtedly, the City Inspector. He is our Health Officer. Great power is placed in his hands to enable him to carry out whatever designs he may consider necessary in the performance of his duties.
